titles.title: Dismissing the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the Ninth Congressional District of Tennessee.

action.text: The House Committee on House Administration reported an original measure, H. Rept. 113-132, by Mrs. Miller (MI).

calendar.text: Placed on the House Calendar, Calendar No. 36.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: 6/26/2013--Passed House without amendment. Dismisses the election contest relating to the office of Representative from the 9th congressional district of Tennessee.
